1、检查前置条件

系统版本：ubuntu 14.04 以上
$ uname -a
Linux ubt14043 3.19.0-25-generic #26~14.04.1-Ubuntu SMP Fri Jul 24 21:16:20 UTC 2015 x86_64 x86_64 x86_64 GNU/Linux

安装内核
$ sudo apt-get install linux-headers-3.13.0-43-generic
$ sudo apt-get install linux-image-3.13.0-43-generic
$ sudo apt-get install linux-headers-3.13.0-43
$ sudo update-grub
$ ls -l /sys/class/misc/device-mapper
lrwxrwxrwx 1 root root 0 Jul 23 16:11 /sys/class/misc/device-mapper -> ../../devices/virtual/misc/device-mapper
